author: StarTalk
description:
Was the universe created by a God? Neil deGrasse Tyson and Chuck Nice discuss The Fine-Tuning Argument, Intelligent Design, and breaks down the different ideations of God. We explore different definitions of God and even Chuck’s past as a preacher.

15:43 - Need for Spirituality
22:51 - Chuck’s Preacher Days
26:22 - Closing
